about: Hi My name is Dylan Bienstock and I want to welcome to my personal website. I am a current undergraduate student at Dartmouth College pursuing a major in Computer Science and a minor in Engineering. I am originally from Santa Barbara, CA but made the daring move across the country to Hanover, NH. On campus I am a part of Dartmouth's Club Water Polo and Club Swim as well as an active member of Dartmouth Hillel. In addition, I spend my winter teaching snowboarding on Dartmouth's very own ski moutain where I am a certfied AASI Snowboard Instructor. Lastly, I was hired as a Teacher's Assistent for Computer Science 10: Problem Solving via Object Oriented Programming, where I hold office hours, lead recitation sections, and grade projects and exams
